Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:44.67,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.74,0:00:51.70,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.77,0:00:55.13,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.13,0:00:59.14,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:03.96,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.70,0:01:11.78,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:18.93,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.23,0:01:25.55,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:33.21,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Didn't I say this would be easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.41,0:02:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A Simile Simoun is nothing more than an imitation Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have Tempus Spatium's blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.92,0:02:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't draw the light trails for a Ri Maajon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.59,0:03:02.60,Titles,,0,0,0,,The Blue Spring
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful line...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a good look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Maaju isn't just a practice exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.49,0:03:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A Simoun is controlled by your body and mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Erii?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Your clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.08,0:03:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the last time... that I'll ever see something this beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Emerald Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.61,0:03:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this what flying a real Simoun is like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Among the volunteers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.34,0:04:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a volunteer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.76,0:04:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.72,0:04:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Deliberately joining at a time like this, knowing that she'd be going into battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you with Tempest too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.27,0:05:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe nobody else sortied with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But I {\i1}singlehandedly—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You went out of your way to mimic the Emerald Ri Maajon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how do you think Neviril would feel if she saw that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Did I do some kind of Ri Maajon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And who's Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,When a Simoun sibylla flies, we call it "praying to the sky."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't use words like "sortie."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's this Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril is the regina of Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sibylla Aurea! The "Golden Priestess!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be her pair!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.11,0:05:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not? She's the best Simoun pilot, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"Simoun 'pilot?'"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.15,0:06:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, at least up till now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.32,0:06:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you're incredible! I think I'm in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wanna be my pair?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So where's Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.04,0:06:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This brings back memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Back when we were cadets, helping you made me so happy I couldn't stand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I still feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.55,0:07:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Those clothes... you're leaving the ship too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.22,0:07:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My seventeenth birthday passed a long time ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.47,0:07:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm thinking about going to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have one last request...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared of going to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wouldn't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Erii.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.49,0:07:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.96,0:07:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there someone named Neviril here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.34,0:07:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Please use her title when you refer to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you, um... Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Chor Tempest's maintenance hangar, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril, are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.81,0:07:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the dining hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:07:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the ballroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Neviril here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the forward observation platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.24,0:08:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Erii said that she's going to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't have a pair anymore, so I'll be accompanying her instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's true, why are you taking your suitcase?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I still haven't sorted out my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I... may enter the Spring, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If that happens, then—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.73,0:08:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That would mean having Tempus Spatium make you a man or a woman, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.24,0:08:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be your pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.54,0:09:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only be a Simoun pilot when you're not a man or a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That means only now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go to the Spring, you won't be able to be my pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't going to happen anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My seventeenth birthday was more than a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You are an outstanding Simoun sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Our country can't afford to lose you in its hour of need.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You have Onashia's permission not to go to the Spring, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.57,0:09:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,People are all originally born female.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.71,0:09:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,However, for society to function properly, it is necessary for half of the people to become men.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how Tempus Spatium chose to create the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:10:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,When we reach our seventeenth birthday, we can choose our sex in the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But Simoun sibyllae can postpone that choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Holy Land is being invaded by other countries without provocation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing that can stop them are the Simoun, and you, the sibyllae who speak to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Those of you who wish to may postpone their visit to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.21,0:10:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, if you truly wish to go, I cannot stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest was terribly hurt for the first time when the fighting began, as was Chor Caput.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Those of you who have reached the age of seventeen... ...are free to make the same choice as Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, {\i1}I'm{\i0} not going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't decided whether to become a man or a woman yet, and I don't {\i1}want{\i0} to decide either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I keep fighting in a Simoun, I don't have to go to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:11:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I came here. Aren't you all the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.79,0:11:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not! When you're old enough to go to the Spring, you should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it means to become an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.25,0:11:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that they need us right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've all decided already whether you're gonna be a man or a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you decided, Nee-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.54,0:11:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right, Erii.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.12,0:11:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,For this one last flight, would you be my pair?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.63,0:11:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just until we get down to the Grand Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get the Simoun ready, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? How's my piloting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call it "piloting." You're "speaking to the Simoun."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.61,0:12:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'm just so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've ever touched a real Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to fly one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you understand, of all people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.42,0:12:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is... different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Because your prayers in the sky aren't for Tempus Spatium anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but for fighting instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.39,0:12:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter to me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The battlefield... you have no idea what it's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I do know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:13:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a cadet on the southern front.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.16,0:13:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Before the war started, most sibyllae went to the Spring as soon as they turned seventeen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But now the Grand Temple says that we don't have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.88,0:13:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we're winning the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What a rude girl. She flew auriga, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She made {\i1}you{\i0} be the sagitta?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the best auriga in the entire country!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.42,0:13:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anyone else here over seventeen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:14:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is Paraietta the only one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nee-san, next month you'll be seventeen too, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's coming up pretty soon for all of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to go after Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.31,0:14:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You decided you were going to become a man for her a long time ago, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I still have things to do here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.69,0:15:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you made up your mind, Erii?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,About what you're going to choose at the Spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.96,0:15:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always been a girl, so I think staying that way would be the most natural,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but I also feel like I might want to try being a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, if I don't become a man, it'll limit my career choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you must be tired, Simoun sibylla, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.61,0:15:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A Simoun sibylla. How beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We beg you, priestess, please lead our country to a bright future.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.12,0:15:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure flying will be fun with you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,For safely completing your prayers, we congratulate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,For protecting us thus far, you have our deepest gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.24,0:17:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.37,0:17:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep trying to imagine myself as a man or a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:18:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What will happen if I can't make a decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Erii.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.34,0:18:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Onashia...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Oracle Onashia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.85,0:18:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My seventeenth birthday is past, and my visit long delayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.89,0:18:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I deeply apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Erii.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Enter the Spring, and pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.95,0:19:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do? I can't decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.47,0:19:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Tempus Spatium has given you a holy answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.99,0:20:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, my name is Erif.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.96,0:20:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She said that little by little, my voice will change and my breasts will get smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But nothing's really changed, has it? Nothing at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.34,0:20:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Nothing's changed... Erif.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.80,0:21:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Rodoreamon! This means...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're staying too, Milady?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always been told that I had to be a sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.85,0:21:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If I returned home now, they'd be angry with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's got a reason, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.71,0:21:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think about it, and I can't really make this thing fly by myself, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.16,0:22:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't go to the Spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.45,0:22:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I went.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.62,0:22:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But I changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.84,0:22:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Go higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.18,0:22:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Higher than our ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.55,0:22:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Higher. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.81,0:22:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
